videos.description: Jimmy Butler drives down the lane and gets the and-1 but winces in pain once he hits the floor.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Butler down on the ground in pain after driving for and-1) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Butler down on the ground in pain after driving for and-1

videos.description: Kyle Lowry steps into the long 3-pointer near the logo and cashes it.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lowry shows off range on 3-pointer) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lowry shows off range on 3-pointer

videos.description: Tyler Herro lobs it up to Jimmy Butler who shows off the bounce for the alley-oop dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Butler gets way up for the alley-oop slam) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Butler gets way up for the alley-oop slam

videos.description: Delon Wright gets an and-1 off the rebound, then gets out in transition for a bucket, forcing Miami to take a timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Back-to-back Delon Wright buckets force a Heat timeout) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Back-to-back Delon Wright buckets force a Heat timeout

videos.description: Trae Young steps into the long 3-pointer and nails it from the logo over Bam Adebayo.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Trae cashes logo 3 over Bam) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trae cashes logo 3 over Bam

videos.description: Trae Young fakes out the defense with a no-look pass to John Collins, who splashes the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Trae makes sweet no-look pass to Collins for a 3) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trae makes sweet no-look pass to Collins for a 3

videos.description: Max Strus ties the game with a 3-pointer, much to the enjoyment of Alonzo Mourning and Pat Riley.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mourning nods his head after Strus splashes 3) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mourning nods his head after Strus splashes 3

videos.description: The Heat go on a dominant run as Max Strus makes it 18 straight points with a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Strus' dunk gives Miami an 18-0 run) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Strus' dunk gives Miami an 18-0 run

videos.description: The Heat go on a 21-0 run in the third quarter to turn their deficit into a lead.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Heat go on 21-0 run to take control in Game 3) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Heat go on 21-0 run to take control in Game 3

videos.description: Trae Young goes with the no-look pass to Delon Wright for the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Trae throws sweet no-look pass to Wright for the layup) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trae throws sweet no-look pass to Wright for the layup

videos.description: Trae Young completes the and-1 late to tie it up for the Hawks.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Young ties it with tough and-1) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young ties it with tough and-1

videos.description: P.J. Tucker nails the corner 3-pointer, giving Miami a one-point lead with under a minute left.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tucker knocks down huge 3 late in the 4th) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tucker knocks down huge 3 late in the 4th

videos.description: Trae Young's floater with 4.4 seconds remaining puts the Hawks ahead late to cap off a dramatic win vs. the Heat in Game 3.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ice Trae floats in go-ahead basket in final seconds) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ice Trae floats in go-ahead basket in final seconds

videos.description: Jimmy Butler can't connect from beyond the arc, clinching a crucial victory for the Hawks in Game 3.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Hawks prevail at the buzzer as Jimmy Butler misses jumper) 2022/04/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hawks prevail at the buzzer as Jimmy Butler misses jumper

videos.description: The Hawks outlast the Heat in the fourth quarter to take Game 3 and get back into the series.
